== Using ObservableListContentProvider and
		ObservableMapLabelProvider
	
		If you use
		`WritableList`
		and
		`ObservableListContentProvider`
		you only listens to the changes in the list. You
		can use
		`ObservableMapLabelProvider`
		to listen to changes of the individual objects.
	
	
